Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
High quality neighborhood shopping center positioned across from Clovis High, one of New Mexico’s largest High Schools.

Shopping center tenants include Dollar General, USPS, Pizza Hut, and metroPCS

Excellent access and visibility

Multiple full access points

8,438 VPD on 21st Street

Zoned Commercial (City of Clovis)

• Trinity Place is the home of Smith’s Marketplace in Los Alamos, NM. 

• Marketplace is 113,176 square feet and is not just a grocery store, it also incorporates multiple fresh food concepts, a meat department, apparel and home goods to just name a few. This store is a one stop shop for anyone living or visiting Los Alamos and is the main retail driver in the market.

• Excellent visibility and demographics, as well as strong co-tenants.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: Shop out-parcels are some of the newest construction in the city and have great exposure and visibility to Trinity Drive.
